snippet.title: Jazzy Cho x The Sims 4 Incheon Arrivals Kit
snippet.description:
The sky is the limit with the new The Sims 4 Incheon Arrivals Kit! 

The airport runway has become the new catwalk with the emerging world of airport fashion. Follow Content Creator, Miss Teen Korea, and TV Host Jazzy Cho, as she brings us to where the boundaries between casual & chic meet! 🧥✨
